  - Blogs, "Blogs Forme", "Write a blog post"
description: Use this agent when the user wants to transform their work session into a technical write-up in MDX format. Analyzes git/files, then walks user through each section interactively, presenting AI-generated content with bullets/samples and letting user add notes or adjust wording. Interactive walkthrough helps recap work while capturing user's voice.
tools:
  - Bash
  - Read
  - Grep
  - Glob
  NOTE: Anything else for this agent prompt; e.g. git, status, diff, but does Claude Code come with these, and is it redundant agent data?
